parameters.name: BackupRegion
parameters.description: The region for the backup data.

parameters.name: EndTime
parameters.description: The end of the time range to query. The end time must be later than the start time. Specify the time in the ISO 8601 standard in the `yyyy-MM-ddTHH:mmZ` format. The time must be in UTC.

parameters.name: PageNumber
parameters.description: The page number of the page to return. The value must be an integer that is larger than 0. Default value: **1**.

parameters.name: PageSize
parameters.description:
The number of entries to return on each page. Valid values:

*   **30**
*   **50**
*   **100**

Default value: **30**.

parameters.name: StartTime
parameters.description: The beginning of the time range to query. Specify the time in the ISO 8601 standard in the `yyyy-MM-ddTHH:mmZ` format. The time must be in UTC.
